Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.Command
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ADD, ASSIGN, BLANK, DIV, ENDIF, ENTER, GOTO, IF, INC, MUL, PRINT, SUB, VAR

    abstract class Command
extends java.lang.Object
    all Commands will extend Command so that a linked list of Commands can be built and iterated through, each Command will do all its work in the execute method
